Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.70,0:09:19.20,IN_EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}I'm here always
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.10,0:09:24.90,IN_EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}Never will leave your side
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.50,0:09:28.10,IN_EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}Cry on and on
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.50,0:09:33.10,IN_EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}Let those tears come on down
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.50,0:09:37.80,IN_EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}Tomorrow will come again soon
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.75,0:00:27.50,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}对了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.20,0:00:30.20,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}今天是休息日来着
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.56,0:02:07.80,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}跟大家商量过后 决定今天休息一天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.30,0:02:10.95,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}到昨天为止发生了许多事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.55,0:02:12.80,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}该怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.55,0:02:15.50,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}算是告一段落了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.10,0:02:20.80,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但这是怎么回事 有种很奇怪的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.75,0:02:24.40,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}休息日我都在干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.15,0:02:29.35,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}假日啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.35,0:02:30.80,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.80,0:02:32.00,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}啊 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.95,0:02:36.30,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}放假反而让我不知道干什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.35,0:02:40.15,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}蓝德他很早就出门了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.15,0:02:41.15,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.15,0:02:42.15,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真意外
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.70,0:02:46.30,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是有人会一休息反而起得更早呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.45,0:02:49.30,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你在说这个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.60,0:03:01.75,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这面包真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.75,0:03:05.75,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}烤的火候
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.45,0:03:09.50,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我还掌握不太好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.60,0:03:11.60,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}似乎是在中途改变火的大小就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.15,0:03:13.25,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但我们用的是柴火
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.25,0:03:14.90,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}休息天就别再烧饭啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.65,0:03:17.70,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不是 我是很感激的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.35,0:03:19.35,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.35,0:03:21.63,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}正好我也饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.30,0:03:24.65,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}蓝德说要去哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.35,0:03:26.95,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}他拿着钓竿
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.80,0:03:29.00,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}梦儿和席赫露呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.80,0:03:32.35,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}今天早上还没看到
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.60,0:03:35.05,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}还在房间里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.80,0:03:40.10,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}可能是睡得比较晚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.05,0:03:43.20,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}席赫露哭得很厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.15,0:03:47.25,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}应该会和梦儿谈到马纳多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.60,0:03:50.50,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}莫古索呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.10,0:03:51.95,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.45,0:03:53.80,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我想想
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.00,0:03:57.05,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}维护一下防具吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.65,0:04:00.15,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}上次那场战斗弄坏了不少地方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.85,0:04:02.20,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}武器也很破
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.20,0:04:03.30,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}拿去打磨了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.05,0:04:06.10,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要去取回来才行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.10,0:04:08.30,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这好像和平时没什么两样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.85,0:04:10.35,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}今天可是难得的休息天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.05,0:04:12.75,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哈尔希洛要干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.65,0:04:14.55,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.55,0:04:15.60,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.50,0:04:21.25,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}傍晚在雪莉的酒馆集合对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.20,0:04:23.80,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.30,0:04:31.55,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.85,0:04:38.30,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}席赫露也起来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.80,0:04:42.30,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你喜欢鸟吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.95,0:04:45.95,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}习惯了 不知不觉就...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.75,0:04:47.60,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}唔...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.25,0:04:53.10,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}啊 莫古索他
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.20,0:04:55.85,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}烤了新的面包
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.75,0:04:57.75,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}闻起来很香
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.40,0:04:59.00,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}都飘到这了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.60,0:05:00.50,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.40,0:05:08.65,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在这里 大家有一起看过夕阳
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.80,0:05:17.40,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.67,0:05:21.40,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.95,0:05:22.95,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哈尔希洛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.15,0:05:25.35,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}今后也请多多关照了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.85,0:05:26.95,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯？怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.70,0:05:28.85,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}彼此彼此
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.70,0:05:30.65,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.10,0:05:32.10,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}顺势就说了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.15,0:05:39.50,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}朝阳也很美哦 从这里看的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.45,0:05:43.35,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.25,0:05:45.70,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以才会成为习惯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.25,0:05:48.90,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.05,0:05:53.05,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}席赫露
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.80,0:05:58.05,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}梦儿醒着 起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.65,0:07:05.50,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哈尔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.40,0:07:12.40,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}坐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.30,0:07:23.55,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我住在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.25,0:07:26.30,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这家旅馆里都是女人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.65,0:07:30.30,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}自从离开义勇兵宿舍以后 就一直住在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.15,0:07:32.55,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那么 这里也是...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.55,0:07:33.85,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}露台没事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.30,0:07:48.20,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你们要离开宿舍的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.00,0:07:51.85,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我可以把这里介绍给梦儿和席赫露
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.70,0:07:53.30,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.90,0:07:55.45,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}她们两个应该会高兴的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.55,0:07:59.65,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}虽然 我们已经习惯了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.53,0:08:03.90,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不过总有一天是要离开的 肯定
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.80,0:08:13.50,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}宿舍吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.40,0:08:19.10,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}梅丽住在那个破烂宿舍的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.70,0:08:23.45,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一定是和他最初的同胞们一起的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.40,0:08:30.05,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}和那些现在已经不在了的同伴们一起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.60,0:10:14.50,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}呃 达姆洛？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.65,0:10:18.75,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好像杀气腾腾呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.75,0:10:20.90,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那边的哥布林们
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.90,0:10:24.20,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嘛 不过我只知道他们杀气腾腾的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.20,0:10:25.70,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你是新来的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.70,0:10:26.80,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}人新
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.80,0:10:27.80,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}人新？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.55,0:10:29.90,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}新人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.90,0:10:31.25,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}见习义勇兵吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.25,0:10:32.60,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}没错 就是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.60,0:10:38.85,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那个人新的队伍好像很惨哦 在达姆洛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.85,0:10:40.25,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}很糟哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.25,0:10:44.20,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我们打倒的那只哥布林应该是从新街区来的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.85,0:10:47.70,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}装备和动作都高一个档次
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.40,0:10:49.70,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}因为我们打倒了它...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.70,0:10:51.15,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}没错没错
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.15,0:10:57.65,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}生气的哥布林从新街区大量涌入 怒气冲冲地在巡逻
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.65,0:10:59.80,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那么对我们来说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.80,0:11:01.50,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}暂时不要去管它们
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.50,0:11:03.80,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}该怎么说呢 热气腾腾的蛋糕？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.80,0:11:05.70,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}烫的时候不要去碰啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.10,0:11:09.20,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.20,0:11:11.00,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}呦呦 还好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.00,0:11:12.20,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}干得如何
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.15,0:11:14.55,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}再来两瓶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.55,0:11:16.35,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哥布真惨
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.35,0:11:19.15,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}与其说是哥布林 应该说是达姆洛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.15,0:11:20.00,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你听到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.50,0:11:20.80,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.80,0:11:22.35,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.35,0:11:23.15,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}什么怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.15,0:11:25.50,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我还没开始想的 说实话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.50,0:11:28.90,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}明天本来也打算去达姆洛的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.90,0:11:31.55,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}明天去达姆洛赚不到钱的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.70,0:11:33.95,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哈尔希洛 你可是要负全责的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.95,0:11:35.70,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}什么责任啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.70,0:11:39.30,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我说让你战士点诚意 起码要把你那份报酬给我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.30,0:11:41.80,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}为什么我要做这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.65,0:11:45.70,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}再说了 如果赚不到钱 那报酬也是零啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.60,0:11:49.80,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那个 换个地方打猎怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.45,0:11:54.70,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}赛琳矿山
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.90,0:12:02.25,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}啊 不 抱歉 我自言自语...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.25,0:12:05.75,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哈尔希洛 你偶尔也会提点不错的主意嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.75,0:12:07.60,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}虽说只是偶尔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.60,0:12:09.55,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我当然举双手赞成
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.10,0:12:11.30,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}没事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.80,0:12:14.55,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}赛琳矿山不是有Tetra Pot
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.55,0:12:17.15,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}赏金有30金呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.15,0:12:21.25,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不是Teara Pot 是Dead Spot 还有是赛琳矿山
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.65,0:12:28.00,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不管怎么说 眼下只能换地方了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.55,0:12:33.80,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是别的地方我完全不认识 现在想该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.90,0:12:39.50,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}只要小心不碰上Dead Spot
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.30,0:12:43.60,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一直在同一个地方也太千篇一律了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.00,0:12:47.00,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}会变得像日常刷本一样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.50,0:12:50.15,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}也可能会因此犯下奇怪的错误
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.95,0:12:54.80,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}偶尔还是需要一点刺激和紧张感
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.40,0:13:00.15,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}也是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.05,0:13:01.80,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.80,0:13:05.80,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}想去赛琳矿山
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.30,0:13:09.55,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.95,0:13:11.55,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.40,0:13:15.50,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}每天都一样就这么不好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.35,0:13:18.95,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}最近危险的情况也开始减少了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.45,0:13:21.70,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}钱也一点点存起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.55,0:13:24.40,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}梦儿没有不满
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.00,0:13:28.55,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}唔..只是达姆洛那边的情况...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.55,0:13:29.70,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}对哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.60,0:13:32.55,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那也没办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.30,0:13:37.85,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}猎物变了 心情也会变 说不定不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.35,0:13:41.10,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}梅丽？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.55,0:13:56.30,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}稍微
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.80,0:13:57.80,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}失陪一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.90,0:13:59.60,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}梅丽
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.45,0:15:00.50,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.90,0:15:05.45,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不 我才是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.95,0:15:10.80,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}去赛琳矿山
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.40,0:15:16.65,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}梅丽就不得不踏入失去同伴的现场了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.15,0:15:19.35,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这样她会很难受
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.15,0:15:21.15,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}非常痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.75,0:15:30.50,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我们在那之后其实也基本没有接近过 马纳多去世的那个地方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.20,0:15:36.50,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}连这种地方的存在本身
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.95,0:15:40.60,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}都想要忘记
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.60,0:15:50.00,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}赛琳矿山 去赛琳矿山的话 我高兴不起来 应该
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.95,0:15:52.95,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}现在也是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.95,0:15:56.95,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大概 今后一直都会是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.10,0:15:59.90,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.55,0:16:05.70,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是 这是一定要跨越的坎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.60,0:16:10.00,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不 是我想跨越
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.50,0:16:12.95,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不然我就无法前进
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.28,0:16:18.05,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}可是 我一个人是无法跨越的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.50,0:16:22.15,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要借助别人的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.25,0:16:24.50,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}需要你们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.85,0:16:28.35,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}跟你们一起去 我会很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.95,0:16:36.45,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}因为你们说我是你们的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.35,0:16:41.70,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}虽然可能会给你们添麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.73,0:16:45.35,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不会麻烦的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.05,0:16:49.55,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎么可能是麻烦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.50,0:16:55.30,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哈尔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.30,0:16:57.30,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.75,0:17:01.10,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}可能是因为我很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.30,0:17:04.50,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我真逊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.85,0:17:12.50,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哈尔这样就很好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.70,0:17:21.55,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.80,0:17:38.50,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要去赛琳矿山 必须要做好万全的准备
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.85,0:17:42.40,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}装备 还有技能
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.60,0:17:48.00,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我付了40银 选择了学习偷袭战法中的蜘蛛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.20,0:17:52.65,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那么久开始吧 Old Cat
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.65,0:17:53.90,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.45,0:17:56.75,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}变得这么僵硬
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.75,0:18:00.30,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}硬的只要有你身上挂着的东西就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.30,0:18:03.70,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不 那个并不硬...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.80,0:18:09.20,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}实战的话你的头和身体就已经拜拜了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.80,0:18:12.90,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}没有短刀的话折了你的颈椎也不错
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.10,0:18:19.75,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我先回一直对你使用蜘蛛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.75,0:18:21.35,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}直到你吐血为止
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.40,0:18:24.10,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不会死吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.10,0:18:25.45,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.00,0:18:30.80,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在我的训练下死掉的 至今为止就那几个人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.80,0:18:32.20,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哪几个人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.90,0:18:48.50,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}站不起来了的话就没办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.50,0:18:49.60,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}休息一会儿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.10,0:18:53.25,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}休息的时候也要锻炼哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.25,0:18:55.40,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}腹肌 腹肌
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.40,0:18:59.05,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}还是说改成忍受拷问的训练比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.05,0:19:01.15,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}会死的 真的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.15,0:19:03.75,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那就聊会天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.35,0:19:05.40,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.40,0:19:07.05,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}赶紧聊 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.55,0:19:10.70,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}聊...聊天
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.70,0:19:12.00,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小笑话也行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.00,0:19:14.30,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我想不到这种梗啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.30,0:19:16.35,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你还真是个无聊的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.35,0:19:18.50,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以才没女朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.20,0:19:22.50,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}没...没法否认
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.50,0:19:24.80,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你队伍里也有女人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.65,0:19:27.65,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}有...有三个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.65,0:19:29.20,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好歹搞上一个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.25,0:19:33.40,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不过 全吃了才是王道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.40,0:19:35.65,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不 这种事我有点...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.55,0:19:38.85,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}总归有个在意的女人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.95,0:19:43.05,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你刚才是不是想到了谁的脸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.15,0:19:45.40,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}对...对了老师
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.80,0:19:49.00,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我有事情想跟你商量...问你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.00,0:19:51.25,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}肯定是跟女人有关吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.25,0:19:53.30,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.30,0:19:56.15,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你是想岔开话题
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.15,0:19:58.95,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我没那种精力 真的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.15,0:20:05.00,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.65,0:20:08.05,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这是个不错的征兆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.05,0:20:09.20,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}征兆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.20,0:20:11.70,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是 可别误会了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.70,0:20:13.85,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这不是什么特别的事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.35,0:20:20.30,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不 什么误会不误会的 我都不知道这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.30,0:20:22.10,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真迟钝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.10,0:20:24.40,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你就是只Old Cat
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.40,0:20:25.20,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}迟钝？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.85,0:20:26.80,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}迟钝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.35,0:20:29.80,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是直觉却挺准
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.50,0:20:35.55,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你看到的线 只要积累经验每个人都会看到个一两次
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.20,0:20:41.00,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我的情况是 还没到一天一次那么勤 不过也挺多的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.70,0:20:44.25,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这种情况也有
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.25,0:20:45.80,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}各个人差别很大
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.60,0:20:47.80,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}老师呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.90,0:20:51.40,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}有时看得到有时看不到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.40,0:20:53.80,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}也不是什么集中精力就能看到的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.30,0:20:55.20,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我看
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.40,0:20:59.50,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要提高准确性的话 就要磨练技术
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.50,0:21:00.90,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}还有体力
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.55,0:21:02.75,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是...是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.75,0:21:05.75,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}说自己没精力 就是还差火候
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.75,0:21:26.30,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}看上去只是座山啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.65,0:21:33.70,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}赛琳矿山 是在从前人族的阿拉巴吉亚王国
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.20,0:21:37.45,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}向边境扩张势力时开发的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.80,0:21:46.50,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在无命之王率领的军势 驱逐了人族之后 就由地精一派占领了矿山
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.25,0:21:50.60,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}听说在那之后 他们就一只居住在矿山里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.15,0:21:53.95,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.95,0:21:54.75,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}上吧
